In,an,effort,to,connect,developers,with,the,tools,needed,to,host,and,share,the,Government,s,drug,abuse,research,and,prevention,information,the,National,Institute,on,Drug,Abuse,hosts,an,API,through,which,they,expose,their,Drug,Use,Screening,Tool,The,Drug,Use,Screening,Tool,is,an,interactive,multiple,choice,quize,built,to,help,clinicians,identify,risky,substance,use,in,their,adult,patients,The,API,supports,GET,calls,to,retrieve,questions,and,results,and,POST,calls,to,submit,answers,The,API,will,return,JSONP,formatted,responses,in,plain,text,through,HTTP